.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: mauve, fuchsia, lilac, purple, coral
There are 5 different nationalities: german, argentine, american, indonesian, pakistani
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, ritmeester, davidoff, tiparillo, aristoff
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-almond-milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, sprite, iced-tea
5 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, goldfish, chinchilla, rat

1. the german is the person who likes mauve
2. the argentine is the owner of the mouse
3. the person drinking soy-almond-milk is the person who likes fuchsia
4. the american is the person drinking hot-chocolate
5. the person who likes fuchsia is to the right of the person who likes lilac
6. the siglo-smoker is the owner of the rat
7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who likes purple
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle
9. the indonesian is on the far left
10. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig
11. the ritmeester-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla
12. the tiparillo-smoker is the person drinking sprite
13. the pakistani is the aristoff-smoker
14. the indonesian is to the left or right of the person who likes coral

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   indonesian	|    american	|     german	|    argentine	|    pakistani	|
| Color		|    purple	|      coral	|      mauve	|     lilac	|     fuchsia	|
| Beverage	|     iced-tea	|      hot-chocolate	|      almond-milk	| sprite	|     soy-almond-milk	|
| Cigar		|     ritmeester	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| tiparillo	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     guinea-pig	|     chinchilla	|     rat	|     mouse	|     goldfish	|
